other_tests.findings: No reaction of serum FSH and LH to LHRH; TSH response to TRH was consistent with tertiary hypothyroidism; minimal response of ACTH and cortisol to CRH; minimal response of serum GH with a peak of 0.7 mU/liter.
Small anterior pituitary remnant, no pituitary stalk, and ectopic neurohypophysis.
Maximum of predicted 225 watts reached at a maximum heart rate of 158 beats/min and a maximum blood pressure of 176/60 mm Hg.
Bone age of 16 years according to Greulich and Pyle.
